thread.title: Stacie Byers
thread.title_full: Craft Cuts reviewed by Stacie Byers

author: Stacie Byers
title: Stacie Byers
text: I have ordered stencils 3 times now over the last year to make fabric patterns to sew on my toddlers' t-shirts. I am thrilled with the quality and the prices are truly reasonable. As for shipping, I ordered my last shipment Sunday afternoon 2/5/17 and received it today 2/8/17! I wasn't even expecting it for a few more days, minimum! I'm looking forward to ordering more items from Craft Cuts...they are my new favorite store!
